metadata.name: Unforgettable Indigo : The Hue of Friendship
metadata.description: Indestructible bonds can run into differences that drive us apart. This is what happened to me with my indigo friend. This collage traces two years of collaboration with Luluixixix. I cherish the joy and complicity we shared, hoping that our paths will cross again and that we will rediscover the beautiful color indigo that once united us.
